===Noun===
{{en-noun|pl=acanthuses|pl2=acanthi}}

# {{context|botany}} A member of the genus ''[[Acanthus]]'' of [[herbaceous]] [[prickly]] plants with toothed leaves, (family [[Acanthaceae]], order [[Scrophulariales]]) found in the south of Europe, Asia Minor, and India.{{defdate|First attested in the mid 16th century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{context|architecture}} An ornament resembling the [[foliage]] or leaves of ''[[Acanthus spinosus]]'', and used in the [[capital]]s of the [[Corinthian]] and [[composite]] orders.{{defdate|First attested in the mid 18th century.}}<ref name=SOED/>

